{
  "stem": "10406.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a wall between the two.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's why they probably didn't find it for such a long time because they knew how to look for hiding places, but this looks like it's a wall.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they went to the other side of the house, and they missed it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one of them got suspicious and pushed away the closet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said, I thought there was a door here maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he took the hatchet and hit it into the wood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was another house right ne-- right next to this house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was a tiny alleyway between the two houses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a window going up from that room to the-- between the two houses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And for some reason, I had my eye on that window.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, in case something happens, I'll try to get out of that window.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when I saw the light-- the minute I saw the hatchet coming through, the first light-- we were ly-- basically lying on a bed there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was nothing else to do all day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I had pants on and a-- and a shirt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I did not have shoes on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went for the window just the way I was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I had some things with me that I didn't manage to take, even.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I got out of that window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I made my way to the front.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I got out between the little alleyway between the two houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I see there are people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And suddenly I hear them saying, Jews, Jews, Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I figured they mean me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so I'm waiting for somebody to grab me, and nobody's grabbing me, so I keep walking away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they meant the other Jews that they, they captured.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
